    "html": "<p>Dr Kaninika Panda, Fertility Consultant at Santaan Fertility & Research Centre (Bhubaneswar), will share vital doctor tips for managing endometriosis. Join her live on BIG 92.7 FM  for \"Listen Your Doctor\" – breaking the silence on this common yet often misunderstood condition.</p><p>Event Details</p><p>• Date: 28th March 2026</p><p>• Time: 10:30 hrs  I  17:40 hrs ( 20 Mins )</p><p>• Platform: BIG 92.7 FM Radio</p><p>Endometriosis affects millions, causing pain and fertility challenges. Don't miss expert advice to empower yourself or loved ones. Tune in, listen, and break the silence today! </p><p>#santaan-news #EndometriosisAwareness #WomensHealth #BIGFM</p><br/>",
